      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把柱模型和ROM模板画出来。柱模型用圆角矩形，ROM用六边形表示，这样区分数据源和处理模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Column Model",
        "Reduced-order model template"
